public interface LifecycleTransition
extends DimensionsObject

Represents a Dimensions lifecycle state transition.

addRole

void addRole(java.lang.String roleName,
             boolean optional,
             boolean pending)
             throws DimensionsRuntimeException
Specifies a Dimensions role that is to be authorized to perform the transition.

Parameters:
roleName - the Dimensions role to be authorized to perform the transition.
optional - optional flag for the role. True: actioning an object to the 'from State' does not require the existence of a user holding the role (otherwise, false).
pending - the pending flag for the role. True: the object will appear in the Pending List of the role holders when it is actioned to the 'from State'.
Throws:
DimensionsRuntimeException - if connection error or internal error occurs
